est anyone concerned with wider issues in Asian studies.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 4aAsian Studies. 4aCultural Studies. 4aLeiden University Press. 4aSociology and Social History. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aAsia, Asian Studies, History, Biography, Cultural engagement.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311102374840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789400604445zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789400604445zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789400604445/original  a978-3-11-102374-8 Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA